6. Question: Build an email subscription form with an input field for email and a "Subscribe" 
button that opens the user's default email client when clicked.

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Email-Subscription</title>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="subscription-form">
    <h2>Subscribe to our Newsletter</h2>
    <input type="email" id="email" placeholder="Enter your email" required />
    <button>Subscribe</button>
  </div>

</body>
</html>

